text_block_list.name: Otonashi Etsuko
text_block_list.text: Hmmm… is this your current practice plan? … I see, I see.

text_block_list.name: Otonashi Etsuko
text_block_list.text: Oh, please don't play games with me. This isn't a real plan, is it?

text_block_list.name: Otonashi Etsuko
text_block_list.text: I mean you, trainer. You're still hiding some grand self-sacrificial plan aren't you…!?
